nibli
======

This product bundles third-party software.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ilmentufa camxes (Lojban parser) — nibli-ui/assets/js/vendor/camxes/
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The files `camxes.js`, `camxes_preproc.js`, and `LICENSE` under
`nibli-ui/assets/js/vendor/camxes/` are vendored from the ilmentufa project
(https://github.com/lojban/ilmentufa), pinned at commit
778ea138f7d150121ca722db7536ce3b123943ac. They are used as the local "official"
Lojban grammar gate in the fanva translator.

